text: Grant Thomas Thornton (born 29 August 1992) is an English cricketer. He made his List A debut for Warwickshire in the 2017 Royal London One-Day Cup on 27 April 2017. He made his first-class debut for Warwickshire in the 2017 County Championship on 19 May 2017. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:English cricketers Category:Warwickshire cricketers Category:Sportspeople from Coventry
